.PP
The default behaviour is ignore the message. To get a printout for each message with \fIAlwaysDisplay = true\fR, use for example \fI{ssh_msg_debug_fun, fun(_,true,M,_)-> io:format("DEBUG: ~p~n", [M]) end}\fR


